reviews.text: Love Thai food, try this restaurant. Special dishes available. We are so lucky to have the steam fish on special, it save around $50.
Nice Thai food and good price for lunch set.
A very good Thai restaurant.

I spent 3 hours at this restaurant- 1 Hr waiting to be seated, 1 hour, 15 minutes waiting to be served, 25 minutes eating, 20 minutes waiting for the bill. 

I had fish fillet massaman curry but the fish was almost entirely batter. The curry congealed. 

This is my first google review - the restaurant has afforded me plenty of time to write it
Awesome thai food, taste as good as what I had in Bangkok!

result.adr_address: 香港竹園龍翔道136號
result.name: 亞萊泰

reviews.text: 咖喱食品👍

2019年7月26日中午本人在黃大仙亞萊泰午餐，侍應比杯撩過牙的牙簽水比我飲，上餐時更飛擲D餸過來，D湯汁飛到去D雞度，當時人又唔多，兩個侍應由頭到尾眼厲厲，2019年7月27日，我致電問工作人員張小姐，係咪因為我著中式衣服，以為我係去黃大仙廟既大陸遊客所以玩我？2019年7月31日，佢已承認事實及道歉，於此，我想告訴貴公司，著旗袍也好，漢服也好，希望你地不要令人懷疑你地服裝歧視，我在香港土生土長，你地個日D服務真經典兼嚇死人。
下午茶有多款，黄 咖哩 牛腩飯好加凍飲.
坐位舒適,侍應服務態度良好。不用加ㄧ,食物味道不錯。
味道不錯，價錢亦合理

Big shopping mall in Wong Tai Sin. Lots of good restaurant choices. Clean public bathrooms.
There is an access to the small shopping mall through Exit D of the Wong Tai Sin MTR Station. Many restaurants and food kiosks line the passage way.
The shops here are smaller than those in the north mall.
